<pb n="0520c" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0520c"/>
<lb n="0520c01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0520c02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1457</head>
<lb n="0520c03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>根本說一切有部<note n="0520022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔略〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0520022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔略〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0520022"><lem wit="【大】">略</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>毘奈耶雜事
<lb n="0520c04" ed="T"/>攝頌<note n="0520023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0520023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0520023"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0520c05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0520c06" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0520024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三藏法師＝大唐三藏【宋】【元】【宮】，唐三藏【明】</note><note n="0520024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三藏法師＝大唐三藏【宋】【元】【宮】，＝唐三藏【明】</note><app n="0520024"><lem wit="【大】">三藏法師</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">大唐三藏</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唐三藏</rdg></app>義淨奉　制譯</byline>
<lb n="0520c07" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT24p0520c0701">此<note n="0520025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雜＝近【明】</note><app n="0520025"><lem wit="【大】">雜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">近</rdg></app>事中總有八門，以大門一頌攝盡宏綱，
<lb n="0520c08" ed="T"/>一一門中各有別門，總攝八頌就別門中各
<lb n="0520c09" ed="T"/>有十頌，合九十頌，并內攝頌向有千行。若能
<lb n="0520c10" ed="T"/>讀<note n="0520026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＝頌【明】</note><app n="0520026"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">頌</rdg></app>憶持者，即可總閑其義。</p>
<lb n="0520c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0520c1101">大門總攝頌曰<note place="inline">總有八頌攝</note>：</p>
<lb n="0520c12" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0520c1201"><l>&CB00513;石及牛毛，</l><l>三衣并上座；</l>
<lb n="0520c13" ed="T"/><l>舍利猛獸筋，</l><l>笈多尼除塔。</l></lg>
<lb n="0520c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0520c1401">第一別門總攝頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0520c15" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0520c1501"><l>&CB00513;揩剪爪&CB00425;，</l><l>鏡生支蹈衣；</l>
<lb n="0520c16" ed="T"/><l>水羅生豆殊，</l><l>洗足裙應結。</l></lg>
<lb n="0520c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0520c1701">別門子攝頌十行：</p>
<lb n="0520c18" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0520c1801"><l>&CB00513;揩石白土，</l><l>牛黃香益眼；</l>
<lb n="0520c19" ed="T"/><l>打柱等諸緣，</l><l>瓔珞即應知。</l>
<lb n="0520c20" ed="T"/><l>剪爪髮揩光，</l><l>春時&CB00290;小果；</l>
<lb n="0520c21" ed="T"/><l>渴聽五種藥，</l><l>廣說大生緣。</l>
<lb n="0520c22" ed="T"/><l>綴&CB00425;畜資具，</l><l>刀子及針筒；</l>
<lb n="0520c23" ed="T"/><l>并以&CB01856;有三，</l><l>是大仙開許。</l>
<lb n="0520c24" ed="T"/><l>照鏡并鑒水，</l><l>不應用梳刷；</l>
<lb n="0520c25" ed="T"/><l>頂上留長髮，</l><l>浴室栗&CB01754;毘。</l>
<lb n="0520c26" ed="T"/><l>生支當護面，</l><l>不為歌舞樂；</l>
<lb n="0520c27" ed="T"/><l>許作歌詠聲，</l><l>用&CB00425;有四種。</l>
<lb n="0520c28" ed="T"/><l>蹈衣并諸袋，</l><l>褥及於坐具；</l>
<lb n="0520c29" ed="T"/><l>有緣離三衣，</l><l>六種心念法。</l>
<pb n="0521a" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0521a"/>
<lb n="0521a01" ed="T"/><l>水羅有五種，</l><l>器共一衣食；</l>
<lb n="0521a02" ed="T"/><l>露形噉飲食，</l><l>洗浴事應知。</l>
<lb n="0521a03" ed="T"/><l>豆生不淨地，</l><l>吐食指授索；</l>
<lb n="0521a04" ed="T"/><l>銅器不應為，</l><l>盛鹽等隨畜。</l>
<lb n="0521a05" ed="T"/><l>應為洗足處，</l><l>及以濯足盆；</l>
<lb n="0521a06" ed="T"/><l>熱時須扇風，</l><l>蚊蟲開五拂。</l>
<lb n="0521a07" ed="T"/><l>結下裙不高，</l><l>不持於重擔；</l>
<lb n="0521a08" ed="T"/><l>若病許杖絡，</l><l>服蒜等隨聽。</l></lg>
<lb n="0521a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0521a0901">第二別門總攝頌曰<note n="0521001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔十行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521001"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">十行</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>：</p>
<lb n="0521a10" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0521a1001"><l>牛毛并傘蓋，</l><l>披緂勝鬘緣，</l>
<lb n="0521a11" ed="T"/><l>出家藥湯瓶，</l><l>門扇鎚斤斧。</l></lg>
<lb n="0521a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0521a1201">別門子攝頌十行：</p>
<lb n="0521a13" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0521a1301"><l>牛毛及隱處，</l><l>同床不獨<note n="0521002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">披＝被【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">披＝被【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521002"><lem wit="【大】">披</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">被</rdg></app>；</l>
<lb n="0521a14" ed="T"/><l>若得白色衣，</l><l>染覆方應用。</l>
<lb n="0521a15" ed="T"/><l>傘蓋無後世，</l><l>歌聲不放火；</l>
<lb n="0521a16" ed="T"/><l>遊行覓依止，</l><l>毛緂不翻披。</l>
<lb n="0521a17" ed="T"/><l>披緂聽不聽，</l><l>惡聲不置&CB00425;；</l>
<lb n="0521a18" ed="T"/><l>衣開<note n="0521003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三種紐＝五種紉【明】</note><app n="0521003"><lem wit="【大】">三種紐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">五種紉</rdg></app>，</l><l>應知<note n="0521004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">條＝修【宮】</note><app n="0521004"><lem wit="【大】">條</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">修</rdg></app>亦三。</l>
<lb n="0521a19" ed="T"/><l>勝鬘惡生事，</l><l>次制諸瓔珞；</l>
<lb n="0521a20" ed="T"/><l>金<note n="0521005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">條＝絛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">條＝絛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521005"><lem wit="【大】">條</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">絛</rdg></app>及彩物，</l><l>斯皆不應畜。</l>
<lb n="0521a21" ed="T"/><l>出家有五利，</l><l>不捉錢授學；</l>
<lb n="0521a22" ed="T"/><l>大眾說伽他，</l><l>&CB00195;<note n="0521006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">筩＝筒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">筩＝筒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521006"><lem wit="【大】">筩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">筒</rdg></app>漱聽許。</l>
<lb n="0521a23" ed="T"/><l>藥湯應洗浴，</l><l>灌鼻開銅盞；</l>
<lb n="0521a24" ed="T"/><l>乘輿老病聽，</l><l>須知便利事。</l>
<lb n="0521a25" ed="T"/><l>水瓶知淨觸，</l><l>願世尊長壽；</l>
<lb n="0521a26" ed="T"/><l>因斯尼涅槃，</l><l>噉嚼俱開五。</l>
<lb n="0521a27" ed="T"/><l>安門扇<note n="0521007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01894;＝鈕【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01894;＝鈕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521007"><lem wit="【大】">&CB01894;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">鈕</rdg></app>孔，</l><l>皮替處中&CB00275;；</l>
<lb n="0521a28" ed="T"/><l>內闊網扇樞，</l><l>開<note n="0521008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">店＝扂【宋】【宮】，居【元】【明】</note><note n="0521008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">店＝扂【宋】【宮】，＝居【元】【明】</note><app n="0521008"><lem wit="【大】">店</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">扂</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">居</rdg></app>須<note n="0521009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羊＝半【宮】</note><app n="0521009"><lem wit="【大】">羊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">半</rdg></app>甲。</l>
<lb n="0521a29" ed="T"/><l>鐵鎚及鎗子，</l><l>鐵<note n="0521010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01916;＝插【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01916;＝插【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521010"><lem wit="【大】">&CB01916;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">插</rdg></app>并木杴；</l>
<pb n="0521b" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0521b"/>
<lb n="0521b01" ed="T"/><l>釜床&CB01105;五百，</l><l>斧鑿眾皆許。</l>
<lb n="0521b02" ed="T"/><l>許斤斧三梯，</l><l>竹木繩隨事；</l>
<lb n="0521b03" ed="T"/><l>下灌造寺法，</l><l>說難<note n="0521011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＝陀【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他＝陀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521011"><lem wit="【大】">他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">陀</rdg></app>因緣。</l></lg>
<lb n="0521b04" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0521b0401">第三別門總攝頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0521b05" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0521b0501"><l>三衣及衣架，</l><l>河邊造寺鹽，</l>
<lb n="0521b06" ed="T"/><l>拭面拭身巾，</l><l>寺座刀應畜。</l></lg>
<lb n="0521b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0521b0701">別門子攝頌十行：</p>
<lb n="0521b08" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0521b0801"><l>三衣條葉量，</l><l>床&CB00560;拂遊塵；</l>
<lb n="0521b09" ed="T"/><l>行處著&CB01071;&CB00544;，</l><l><note n="0521012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">扞＝&CB01798;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">扞＝&CB01798;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521012"><lem wit="【大】">扞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&CB01798;</rdg></app>石須時畜。</l>
<lb n="0521b10" ed="T"/><l>衣架及燈籠，</l><l>勿使蟲傷損；</l>
<lb n="0521b11" ed="T"/><l>熱開三面舍，</l><l>可記難陀身。</l>
<lb n="0521b12" ed="T"/><l>河邊制齒木，</l><l>羅怙遣出門；</l>
<lb n="0521b13" ed="T"/><l>合訶不合訶，</l><l>二行應與服。</l>
<lb n="0521b14" ed="T"/><l>造寺安簷網，</l><l>廣陳掃地緣；</l>
<lb n="0521b15" ed="T"/><l>求法說二童，</l><l>熱時聽造舍。</l>
<lb n="0521b16" ed="T"/><l>石鹽安<note n="0521013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">角＝筒【宮】</note><app n="0521013"><lem wit="【大】">角</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">筒</rdg></app>內，</l><l>藥器用&CB01071;&CB00544;；</l>
<lb n="0521b17" ed="T"/><l>安替誦經時，</l><l>以物承其足。</l>
<lb n="0521b18" ed="T"/><l>拭面巾&CB00520;薄，</l><l>唾盆并襯體；</l>
<lb n="0521b19" ed="T"/><l>鐵槽砌基地，</l><l>日光珠浣衣。</l>
<lb n="0521b20" ed="T"/><l>拭身履<note n="0521014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蛇＝地【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蛇＝地【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521014"><lem wit="【大】">蛇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">地</rdg></app>咽，</l><l>石器生疑惑；</l>
<lb n="0521b21" ed="T"/><l>染衣有多種，</l><l>隨意盡伽藍。</l>
<lb n="0521b22" ed="T"/><l>造寺所須物，</l><l>穿床禮敬儀；</l>
<lb n="0521b23" ed="T"/><l>別畜剃<note n="0521015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">髮＝鬘【元】【明】</note><app n="0521015"><lem wit="【大】">髮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">鬘</rdg></app>衣，</l><l>花<note n="0521016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬘＝髮【元】【明】</note><app n="0521016"><lem wit="【大】">鬘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">髮</rdg></app><note n="0521017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">掛＝挂【宮】</note><app n="0521017"><lem wit="【大】">掛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">挂</rdg></app>眠處。</l>
<lb n="0521b24" ed="T"/><l>好座并床施，</l><l>香泥及&CB00425;籠；</l>
<lb n="0521b25" ed="T"/><l>油器法語行，</l><l>衣袋持三索。</l>
<lb n="0521b26" ed="T"/><l>須剃刀應畜，</l><l>及剪甲等物；</l>
<lb n="0521b27" ed="T"/><l>支床并偃<note n="0521018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枕＝机【三】</note><note n="0521018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">枕＝机【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0521018"><lem wit="【大】">枕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">机</rdg></app>，</l><l>香土用隨情。</l></lg>
<lb n="0521b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0521b2801">第四別門總攝頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0521b29" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0521b2901"><l>上座及牆柵，</l><l>緣破并養病，</l>
<pb n="0521c" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0521c"/>
<lb n="0521c01" ed="T"/><l>旃荼&CB00337;蔗寺，</l><l>&CB00425;依栽樹法。</l></lg>
<lb n="0521c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0521c0201">別門子攝頌十行：</p>
<lb n="0521c03" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0521c0301"><l>上座翻次說，</l><l>或可共至終；</l>
<lb n="0521c04" ed="T"/><l>濾作非時漿，</l><l>處不為限齊。</l>
<lb n="0521c05" ed="T"/><l>牆柵尼剃具，</l><l>不著打光衣；</l>
<lb n="0521c06" ed="T"/><l>得少亦平分，</l><l>洗淨儀應識。</l>
<lb n="0521c07" ed="T"/><l>緣破須縫<note n="0521019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01767;＝替【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01767;＝替【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521019"><lem wit="【大】">&CB01767;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">替</rdg></app>，</l><l>明月聞便頌；</l>
<lb n="0521c08" ed="T"/><l>依止知差別，</l><l>三人共坐聽。</l>
<lb n="0521c09" ed="T"/><l>養病除性罪，</l><l>將圓不昇樹；</l>
<lb n="0521c10" ed="T"/><l>王臣不受戒，</l><l>斬手不應為。</l>
<lb n="0521c11" ed="T"/><l>旃荼蘇陀夷，</l><l>大衣暫時用；</l>
<lb n="0521c12" ed="T"/><l>師謨婆蘇達，</l><l>取&CB00425;已物想。</l>
<lb n="0521c13" ed="T"/><l>阿市多護月，</l><l>賊想取<note n="0521020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白＝自【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">白＝自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521020"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">自</rdg></app>衣；</l>
<lb n="0521c14" ed="T"/><l>此與大律同，</l><l>故更不煩出。</l>
<lb n="0521c15" ed="T"/><l>&CB00337;蔗多羅果，</l><l>毛緂黑喜還；</l>
<lb n="0521c16" ed="T"/><l>安置刀子針，</l><l>不用琉璃器。</l>
<lb n="0521c17" ed="T"/><l>寺中應遍<note n="0521021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畫＝盡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0521021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畫＝盡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0521021"><lem wit="【大】">畫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">盡</rdg></app>，</l><l>然火并洗浴；</l>
<lb n="0521c18" ed="T"/><l>&CB00425;水不蹈葉，</l><l>連鞋食不應。</l>
<lb n="0521c19" ed="T"/><l>無&CB00425;度大賊，</l><l>安居無依止；</l>
<lb n="0521c20" ed="T"/><l>五年同利養，</l><l>負重不應為。</l>
<lb n="0521c21" ed="T"/><l>四依求六物，</l><l>賊盜苾芻衣；</l>
<lb n="0521c22" ed="T"/><l>委寄五種殊，</l><l>須知染衣法。</l>
<lb n="0521c23" ed="T"/><l>須知栽樹法，</l><l>賊緂作神通；</l>
<lb n="0521c24" ed="T"/><l>若得上帔衣，</l><l>不應割去&CB01776;。</l></lg>
<lb n="0521c25" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0521c2501">第五別門總攝頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0521c26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0521c2601"><l>焚屍詰三轉，</l><l>捨墮我身亡；</l>
<lb n="0521c27" ed="T"/><l>界苾芻不應，</l><l>不合五皮用。</l></lg>
<lb n="0521c28" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0521c2801">別門子攝頌十行：</p>
<lb n="0521c29" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0521c2901"><l>焚屍誦三啟，</l><l>目連因打亡；</l>
<pb n="0522a" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0522a"/>
<lb n="0522a01" ed="T"/><l>不應廣大作，</l><l>多護諸珍寶。</l>
<lb n="0522a02" ed="T"/><l>詰問令憶念，</l><l>問彼容許不；</l>
<lb n="0522a03" ed="T"/><l>教授事不為，</l><l>長淨及隨意。</l>
<lb n="0522a04" ed="T"/><l>佛三轉法輪，</l><l>初度五人已；</l>
<lb n="0522a05" ed="T"/><l>不喚名族等，</l><l>拘尸宣略教。</l>
<lb n="0522a06" ed="T"/><l>捨墮物不分，</l><l>蚊幬隨意畜；</l>
<lb n="0522a07" ed="T"/><l>三股狀作釜，</l><l>應張羯恥那。</l>
<lb n="0522a08" ed="T"/><l>亡後囑授別，</l><l>委寄者身死；</l>
<lb n="0522a09" ed="T"/><l>他方通委寄，</l><l>若死對餘人。</l>
<lb n="0522a10" ed="T"/><l>界外不與欲，</l><l>將行不展轉；</l>
<lb n="0522a11" ed="T"/><l>說戒隨意事，</l><l>違者並招愆。</l>
<lb n="0522a12" ed="T"/><l>苾芻應知數，</l><l>隨意任行籌；</l>
<lb n="0522a13" ed="T"/><l>不與俗同坐，</l><l>老少應隨夏。</l>
<lb n="0522a14" ed="T"/><l>不應居貯座，</l><l>不誘他求寂；</l>
<lb n="0522a15" ed="T"/><l>不為誓賭物，</l><l>亦不食虎殘。</l>
<lb n="0522a16" ed="T"/><l>不合自藏身，</l><l>不為言白等；</l>
<lb n="0522a17" ed="T"/><l>若得上價<note n="0522001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶＝緂【三】</note><note n="0522001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶＝緂【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0522001"><lem wit="【大】">寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">緂</rdg></app>，</l><l>賣之應共分。</l>
<lb n="0522a18" ed="T"/><l>五皮不應用，</l><l>餘類亦同然；</l>
<lb n="0522a19" ed="T"/><l>若患痔病時，</l><l>熊皮履應著。</l></lg>
<lb n="0522a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0522a2001">第六<note n="0522002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔門〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0522002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔門〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0522002"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>總攝頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0522a21" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0522a2101"><l>猛獸筋不應，</l><l>燈光及勇健；</l>
<lb n="0522a22" ed="T"/><l>馱索度尼法，</l><l>因許喬答彌。</l>
<lb n="0522a23" ed="T"/><l>尼不前長者，</l><l>可與餘臥具；</l>
<lb n="0522a24" ed="T"/><l>不合輒灒水，</l><l>是總頌應知。</l></lg>
<lb n="0522a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0522a2501">別門子攝頌十行：</p>
<lb n="0522a26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0522a2601"><l>猛獸筋皮<note n="0522003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綖＝線【三】【宮】</note><note n="0522003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綖＝線【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0522003"><lem wit="【大】">綖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">線</rdg></app>，</l><l>擁前復擁後；</l>
<lb n="0522a27" ed="T"/><l>兩角及尖頭，</l><l>諸靴皆不合。</l>
<lb n="0522a28" ed="T"/><l>四大王初誕，</l><l>光明<note n="0522004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">普＝並【三】【宮】</note><note n="0522004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">普＝並【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0522004"><lem wit="【大】">普</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">並</rdg></app>皆照；</l>
<lb n="0522a29" ed="T"/><l>父母因斯事，</l><l>各為立其名。</l>
<pb n="0522b" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0522b"/>
<lb n="0522b01" ed="T"/><l>腹中天守護，</l><l>生已蹈蓮花；</l>
<lb n="0522b02" ed="T"/><l>舉手獨稱尊，</l><l>灌洗花衣落。</l>
<lb n="0522b03" ed="T"/><l>阿私多&CB00418;相，</l><l>那剌陀勸師；</l>
<lb n="0522b04" ed="T"/><l>五百瑞現前，</l><l>父王立三字。</l>
<lb n="0522b05" ed="T"/><l>付母養太子，</l><l>令觀大人相；</l>
<lb n="0522b06" ed="T"/><l>阿私多遠至，</l><l>親&CB00418;牟尼形。</l>
<lb n="0522b07" ed="T"/><l>燈光得為王，</l><l>有五<note n="0522005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">珠＝株【三】，殊【宮】</note><note n="0522005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">珠＝株【宋】【元】【明】，＝殊【宮】</note><app n="0522005"><lem wit="【大】">珠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">株</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">殊</rdg></app>勝物；</l>
<lb n="0522b08" ed="T"/><l>因敘奇異事，</l><l>廣說健陀羅。</l>
<lb n="0522b09" ed="T"/><l>鵂鶹鶴飲乳，</l><l>芒草尾身齊；</l>
<lb n="0522b10" ed="T"/><l>斑駁與毛同，</l><l>沙盆水不溢。</l>
<lb n="0522b11" ed="T"/><l>鹽&CB00595;水差別，</l><l>衣瓦變成塵；</l>
<lb n="0522b12" ed="T"/><l>是謂健陀羅，</l><l>世間思十事。</l>
<lb n="0522b13" ed="T"/><l>猛<note n="0522006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光＝虎【明】</note><app n="0522006"><lem wit="【大】">光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">虎</rdg></app>親問母，</l><l>知從蠍所生；</l>
<lb n="0522b14" ed="T"/><l>與彼五百金，</l><l>驅之令出國。</l>
<lb n="0522b15" ed="T"/><l>猛光<note n="0522007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侍＝持【元】【明】</note><app n="0522007"><lem wit="【大】">侍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">持</rdg></app>縛迦，</l><l>金光醫羅&CB00425;；</l>
<lb n="0522b16" ed="T"/><l>那<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="K06n0022_p0943c10" wit="【CBETA】【麗】【磧砂】" cf2="Q06_p0197c25">剌</lem><rdg wit="【大】">刺</rdg></app>陀得果，</l><l>妙髮&CB00425;持油。</l>
<lb n="0522b17" ed="T"/><l>樓上逢增長，</l><l>婬女夜觀星；</l>
<lb n="0522b18" ed="T"/><l>因作馬鳴聲，</l><l>商人抱枯骨。</l>
<lb n="0522b19" ed="T"/><l>牛護獵師死，</l><l>放宮天授歸；</l>
<lb n="0522b20" ed="T"/><l>猛光向得叉，</l><l>殺人聲<note n="0522008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝八【宋】【元】，入【明】</note><note n="0522008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝八【宋】【元】，＝入【明】</note><app n="0522008"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">八</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入</rdg></app>夢。</l>
<lb n="0522b21" ed="T"/><l>猛光一切施，</l><l>影勝捨餅初；</l>
<lb n="0522b22" ed="T"/><l>臥具謂給孤，</l><l>善賢造僧寺。</l>
<lb n="0522b23" ed="T"/><l>文鳩死赤體，</l><l>三種難不應；</l>
<lb n="0522b24" ed="T"/><l>觀無厭不眠，</l><l>總收其七頌。</l>
<lb n="0522b25" ed="T"/><l>林內<note n="0522009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">文＝父【宮】</note><app n="0522009"><lem wit="【大】">文</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">父</rdg></app>鳩死，</l><l>樹下獼猴亡；</l>
<lb n="0522b26" ed="T"/><l>此世他世中，</l><l>四盲闇應識。</l>
<lb n="0522b27" ed="T"/><l>赤體空無用，</l><l>杵臼唯應一；</l>
<lb n="0522b28" ed="T"/><l>患害起疑心，</l><l>輕賤事須漸。</l>
<lb n="0522b29" ed="T"/><l>三種愚癡人，</l><l>離間有三別；</l>
<pb n="0522c" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0522c"/>
<lb n="0522c01" ed="T"/><l>下品應車裂，</l><l>姦詐事應知。</l>
<lb n="0522c02" ed="T"/><l>難得為他事，</l><l>孤獨事多虛；</l>
<lb n="0522c03" ed="T"/><l>相違合重打，</l><l>失去行無益。</l>
<lb n="0522c04" ed="T"/><l>不應事不觀，</l><l>不善合驅&CB00230;；</l>
<lb n="0522c05" ed="T"/><l>驚怖不歡捨，</l><l>渴憶難思憂。</l>
<lb n="0522c06" ed="T"/><l>無厭可愛事，</l><l>不共戲奪財；</l>
<lb n="0522c07" ed="T"/><l>不共爭惡心，</l><l>無依伴不信。</l>
<lb n="0522c08" ed="T"/><l>不睡及不欲，</l><l>九惱無悲心；</l>
<lb n="0522c09" ed="T"/><l>十惡十相違，</l><l>十力天人現。</l>
<lb n="0522c10" ed="T"/><l>勇健與寶器，</l><l>妙光<note n="0522010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘭若中＝五百錢【宮】</note><app n="0522010"><lem wit="【大】">蘭若中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">五百錢</rdg></app>；</l>
<lb n="0522c11" ed="T"/><l>因能活開醫，</l><l>不度損眾者。</l>
<lb n="0522c12" ed="T"/><l>馱索等三同，</l><l>忘由緒并問；</l>
<lb n="0522c13" ed="T"/><l>大神通大藥，</l><l>刀子下天宮。</l>
<lb n="0522c14" ed="T"/><l>度尼<note n="0522011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八＝以【宮】</note><app n="0522011"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">以</rdg></app>敬法，</l><l>尼欲依次坐；</l>
<lb n="0522c15" ed="T"/><l>二部事各殊，</l><l>還俗尼不度。</l>
<lb n="0522c16" ed="T"/><l>近圓從苾芻，</l><l>半月請教授；</l>
<lb n="0522c17" ed="T"/><l>依苾芻坐夏，</l><l>見過不應言。</l>
<lb n="0522c18" ed="T"/><l>不嗔訶禮少，</l><l>意喜而眾中；</l>
<lb n="0522c19" ed="T"/><l>隨意對苾芻，</l><l>斯名八尊法。</l>
<lb n="0522c20" ed="T"/><l>因度喬答彌，</l><l>出家有五利；</l>
<lb n="0522c21" ed="T"/><l>可於五眾內，</l><l>訶責事應知。</l>
<lb n="0522c22" ed="T"/><l>尼不在前行，</l><l>見僧應起敬；</l>
<lb n="0522c23" ed="T"/><l>白僧半<note n="0522012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加＝跏【明】</note><app n="0522012"><lem wit="【大】">加</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">跏</rdg></app>坐，</l><l>歸俗詰無緣。</l>
<lb n="0522c24" ed="T"/><l>長者與殘食，</l><l>殘觸不相避；</l>
<lb n="0522c25" ed="T"/><l>不問隱屑事，</l><l>近圓坐應知。</l>
<lb n="0522c26" ed="T"/><l>苾芻餘臥具，</l><l>應與苾芻尼；</l>
<lb n="0522c27" ed="T"/><l>尼不踏橋板，</l><l>不著裝身物。</l>
<lb n="0522c28" ed="T"/><l>不<note n="0522013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">灒＝讚【宮】</note><app n="0522013"><lem wit="【大】">灒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">讚</rdg></app>水<note n="0522014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">污＝汗【宮】</note><app n="0522014"><lem wit="【大】">污</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">汗</rdg></app>衣，</l><l>不持死胎子；</l>
<lb n="0522c29" ed="T"/><l>不吞於不淨，</l><l>觸已子非他。</l></lg>
<pb n="0523a" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0523a"/>
<lb n="0523a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523a0101">第七別門總攝頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0523a02" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0523a0201"><l>笈多尼不住，</l><l>僧&CB00560;<note n="0523001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">崎＝踦【明】＊</note><app n="0523001"><lem wit="【大】">崎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">踦</rdg></app>二形，</l>
<lb n="0523a03" ed="T"/><l>道小羯磨<note n="0523002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沽＝活【明】</note><app n="0523002"><lem wit="【大】">沽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">活</rdg></app>，</l><l>轉根寺外石。</l></lg>
<lb n="0523a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523a0401">別門子攝頌十行：</p>
<lb n="0523a05" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0523a0501"><l>笈多共兒宿，</l><l>王舍<note n="0523003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藥＝樂【明】</note><app n="0523003"><lem wit="【大】">藥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">樂</rdg></app>叉神；</l>
<lb n="0523a06" ed="T"/><l>施兒衣繫<note n="0523004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">項＝頂【三】</note><note n="0523004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">項＝頂【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0523004"><lem wit="【大】">項</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">頂</rdg></app>，</l><l>稱名與祭食。</l>
<lb n="0523a07" ed="T"/><l>尼不住蘭若，</l><l>不居城外寺；</l>
<lb n="0523a08" ed="T"/><l>不許門前望，</l><l>亦不<note n="0523005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">現＝視【三】【宮】</note><note n="0523005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">現＝視【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0523005"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">視</rdg></app>&CB00275;中。</l>
<lb n="0523a09" ed="T"/><l>許著僧&CB00560;<app type="＊" source="0523001"><lem wit="【大】">崎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">踦</rdg></app>，</l><l>有男<note n="0523006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不池＝池不【三】</note><note n="0523006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不池＝池不【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0523006"><lem wit="【大】">不池</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">池不</rdg></app>浴；</l>
<lb n="0523a10" ed="T"/><l>交衢不應越，</l><l>宜在一邊行。</l>
<lb n="0523a11" ed="T"/><l>若是二形女，</l><l>或是合道類；</l>
<lb n="0523a12" ed="T"/><l>或常血流出，</l><l><note n="0523007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">及＝若【明】</note><app n="0523007"><lem wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">若</rdg></app><note n="0523008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝是【宮】</note><app n="0523008"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">是</rdg></app>無血人。</l>
<lb n="0523a13" ed="T"/><l>道小著內衣，</l><l>近苾芻不唾；</l>
<lb n="0523a14" ed="T"/><l>僧尼不對說，</l><l>當於自眾邊。</l>
<lb n="0523a15" ed="T"/><l>苾芻作羯磨，</l><l>尼可用心聽；</l>
<lb n="0523a16" ed="T"/><l>敷座令人坐，</l><l>尼座應分別。</l>
<lb n="0523a17" ed="T"/><l><note n="0523009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酤＝沾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0523009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">酤＝沾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0523009"><lem wit="【大】">酤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">沾</rdg></app>酒婬女舍，</l><l>途中不觸女；</l>
<lb n="0523a18" ed="T"/><l>隨時開內衣，</l><l>歌舞不應作。</l>
<lb n="0523a19" ed="T"/><l>僧尼根若轉，</l><l>至三皆擯出；</l>
<lb n="0523a20" ed="T"/><l>廣說法與緣，</l><l>蓮花色為<note n="0523010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">使＝便【宮】</note><app n="0523010"><lem wit="【大】">使</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">便</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0523a21" ed="T"/><l>寺外不為懺，</l><l>獨不令剃髮；</l>
<lb n="0523a22" ed="T"/><l>不賃尼寺屋，</l><l>&CB00513;等不揩身。</l>
<lb n="0523a23" ed="T"/><l>不以骨及石，</l><l>若木或拳揩；</l>
<lb n="0523a24" ed="T"/><l>唯用手摩身，</l><l>餘物皆不合。</l></lg>
<lb n="0523a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523a2501">第八門總攝頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0523a26" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0523a2601"><l>除塔懺門前，</l><l>被差不應畜，</l>
<lb n="0523a27" ed="T"/><l>不共女由婦，</l><l>瀉藥三衣蛇。</l></lg>
<lb n="0523a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523a2801">別門子攝頌十行：</p>
<lb n="0523a29" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT24p0523a2901"><l>除塔損波離，</l><l>僧制不應越；</l>
<pb n="0523b" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0523b"/>
<lb n="0523b01" ed="T"/><l>尼無難聽入，</l><l>教誡等相隨。</l>
<lb n="0523b02" ed="T"/><l>尼懺不應輕，</l><l>隨意不長淨；</l>
<lb n="0523b03" ed="T"/><l>更互當收謝，</l><l>尼眾坐應知。</l>
<lb n="0523b04" ed="T"/><l>門前不長淨，</l><l>當須差二尼；</l>
<lb n="0523b05" ed="T"/><l>若至長淨時，</l><l>差人待尼白。</l>
<lb n="0523b06" ed="T"/><l>被差不避去，</l><l>當問教師名；</l>
<lb n="0523b07" ed="T"/><l>著帽為&CB00425;囊，</l><l>結鬘尼不合。</l>
<lb n="0523b08" ed="T"/><l>不應畜銅器，</l><l>變酒合平復；</l>
<lb n="0523b09" ed="T"/><l>賃房與俗旅，</l><l>誑惑作醫巫。</l>
<lb n="0523b10" ed="T"/><l>不共女人浴，</l><l>亦不逆流洗；</l>
<lb n="0523b11" ed="T"/><l>&CB00425;底應安替，</l><l>不畜琉璃盃。</l>
<lb n="0523b12" ed="T"/><l>由婦制錫杖，</l><l>起舞時<note n="0523011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">招＝根【宮】</note><app n="0523011"><lem wit="【大】">招</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">根</rdg></app>罪；</l>
<lb n="0523b13" ed="T"/><l>濕餅受請食，</l><l>說法伴白知。</l>
<lb n="0523b14" ed="T"/><l>瀉藥齒有毒，</l><l>刮舌<note n="0523012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">錍＝篦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0523012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">錍＝篦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0523012"><lem wit="【大】">錍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">篦</rdg></app>應洗；</l>
<lb n="0523b15" ed="T"/><l>由其罪業盡，</l><l>證得阿羅漢。</l>
<lb n="0523b16" ed="T"/><l>三衣隨事<note n="0523013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">著＝者【明】</note><app n="0523013"><lem wit="【大】">著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">者</rdg></app>，</l><l>蘭若法應知；</l>
<lb n="0523b17" ed="T"/><l>浴守門妙花，</l><l>不應<note n="0523014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝作【宮】</note><app n="0523014"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">作</rdg></app>非處。</l>
<lb n="0523b18" ed="T"/><l>由蛇觀臥具，</l><l>一衣不為禮；</l>
<lb n="0523b19" ed="T"/><l>初至寺中時，</l><l>老年應禮四。</l>
<lb n="0523b20" ed="T"/><l>世尊為高勝，</l><l>廣說弟子行；</l>
<lb n="0523b21" ed="T"/><l>行雨問大師，</l><l>為說七六法。</l>
<lb n="0523b22" ed="T"/><l>眾集敬大師，</l><l>聞法生正信；</l>
<lb n="0523b23" ed="T"/><l>自述年衰老，</l><l>說行雨因緣。</l>
<lb n="0523b24" ed="T"/><l>行雨竹林內，</l><l>修理波吒邑；</l>
<lb n="0523b25" ed="T"/><l>渡河詣小<note n="0523015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樹＝村【宮】</note><app n="0523015"><lem wit="【大】">樹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">村</rdg></app>，</l><l>漸向涅槃等。</l></lg>
<lb n="0523b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523b2601">第三十七卷<note n="0523016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">記＝說【明】</note><app n="0523016"><lem wit="【大】">記</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">說</rdg></app>四黑白，次明涅槃事。</p>
<lb n="0523b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523b2701">第三十八說善賢外道得果事，次說諸國爭
<lb n="0523b28" ed="T"/>舍利事。</p>
<lb n="0523b29" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523b2901">第三十九說婆羅門與諸國分舍利，及牛主
<pb n="0523c" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0523c"/>
<lb n="0523c01" ed="T"/>結集事等。</p>
<lb n="0523c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c0201">第四十說五百及七百結集事。</p></div1>
<lb n="0523c03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>根本說一切有部<app type="＊" source="0520022"><lem wit="【大】">略</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>毘奈耶雜事攝頌<app type="＊" source="0520023"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0523c04" ed="T"/><div1 type="w"><p id="pT24p0523c0401"><note n="0523017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此翻場列位依宋元明三本載</note>大唐景龍四年歲次庚戌四月辛巳朔十五
<lb n="0523c05" ed="T"/>日景申，三藏法師大德義淨宣釋梵本並綴
<lb n="0523c06" ed="T"/>文正字</p>
<lb n="0523c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c0701">翻經沙門吐火羅大德達摩秫磨證梵義</p>
<lb n="0523c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c0801">翻經沙門中天竺國大德拔努證梵義</p>
<lb n="0523c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c0901">翻經沙門罽賓國大德達摩難陀證梵文</p>
<lb n="0523c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c1001">翻經沙門淄州大雲寺大德慧沼證義</p>
<lb n="0523c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c1101">翻經沙門洛州崇先寺大德律師道琳證義</p>
<lb n="0523c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c1201">翻經沙門福壽寺寺主大德利明證義</p>
<lb n="0523c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c1301">翻經沙門洛州太平寺大德律師道恪證義</p>
<lb n="0523c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c1401">翻經沙門大薦福寺大德勝莊證義</p>
<lb n="0523c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c1501">翻經沙門相州禪河寺大德玄傘證義筆受</p>
<lb n="0523c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c1601">翻經沙門大薦福寺大德律師智積證義正
<lb n="0523c17" ed="T"/>字。</p>
<lb n="0523c18" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c1801">翻經沙門德州大雲寺寺主慧傘證義</p>
<lb n="0523c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c1901">翻經沙門西涼州伯塔寺大德慧積讀梵本</p>
<lb n="0523c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c2001">翻經婆羅門東天竺國左屯衛翊府中郎將
<lb n="0523c21" ed="T"/>員外置同正員臣瞿金剛證譯</p>
<lb n="0523c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c2201">翻經婆羅門東天竺國大首領臣伊舍羅證
<lb n="0523c23" ed="T"/>梵本</p>
<lb n="0523c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c2401">翻經婆羅門左領軍衛中郎將迦<note n="0523018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">濕＝涅【宮】</note><app n="0523018"><lem wit="【大】">濕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">涅</rdg></app>彌羅
<lb n="0523c25" ed="T"/>國王子臣阿順證譯</p>
<lb n="0523c26" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c2601">翻經婆羅門東天竺國左執戟直中書省臣
<lb n="0523c27" ed="T"/>度頗具讀梵本</p>
<lb n="0523c28" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0523c2801">翻經婆羅門龍播國大達官准五品臣李輸
<lb n="0523c29" ed="T"/>羅證譯</p>
<pb n="0524a" ed="T" id="T24.1457.0524a"/>
<lb n="0524a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0524a0101">金紫光祿大夫守尚書左僕射同中書門下
<lb n="0524a02" ed="T"/>三品上柱國史舒國公臣韋洰源等，及修文
<lb n="0524a03" ed="T"/>館學士三十三人同監</p>
<lb n="0524a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT24p0524a0401">判官朝散大夫行著作佐郎臣劉令植，
<lb n="0524a05" ed="T"/>使金紫光祿大夫<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">祕</lem><rdg wit="【大】">私</rdg></app>書監檢校殿中兼知內
<lb n="0524a06" ed="T"/>外閑&CB01085;隴右三使上柱國嗣號臣王邕</p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>